{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2015/04/travel-in-chengdu/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/entertainment/","name":"生活娱乐活动"}],"tags":[{"name":"同事","path":"/tag/workmate/"},{"name":"大楚网","path":"/tag/dachu/"},{"name":"成都","path":"/tag/chengdu/"},{"name":"旅游","path":"/tag/travel/"},{"name":"陈文","path":"/tag/chen-wen/"}],"featured_media":{"source_url":"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image022.jpg"},"path":"/2015/04/travel-in-chengdu/","date":"2015-04-17T06:57:11.000Z","excerpt":"4月12日武汉～成都坐动车，9个小时啊！美好的第一天就这么过去了，车上在我们大肆比较宽窄巷子与户部巷，想象成都 … ","title":"成都，一个来了就不想走的地方","content":"<p><embed src=\"//static.video.qq.com/TPout.swf?vid=y0156fyzg2z&amp;auto=0\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\"/></p>\n<p>4月12日武汉～成都坐动车，9个小时啊！美好的第一天就这么过去了，车上在我们大肆比较宽窄巷子与户部巷，想象成都美食的时候，旁边一美女不时投来这样的眼神，不过这毫不影响我们疯狂自拍。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/eye.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1790\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/eye.jpg\" alt=\"eye\" width=\"181\" height=\"208\" /></a></p>\n<p>五岳归来不看山，成都回来不吃饭。从到达酒店门口的那一刻，对于味觉的放纵就已经彻底开始。成都的美食不在于去场面华丽的餐厅，街角小巷里买点冒菜，站在路边就能品尝到川味之神韵。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image002.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1779\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image002.jpg\" alt=\"image002\" width=\"1016\" height=\"748\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image002.jpg 1016w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image002-300x221.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image002-782x576.jpg 782w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>成都玩玩全全自由行，听起来蛮爽，可是站在这里吃完要考虑下一站去哪的时候就会成为一个问题，幸好队里有对成都非常熟悉的郑环，“郑导”我们的美好旅程就靠你了！</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image004.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1780\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image004.jpg\" alt=\"image004\" width=\"715\" height=\"402\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image004.jpg 715w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image004-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 715px) 100vw, 715px\" /></a></p>\n<p>坐了一天的车，夜游锦里、武侯祠、耍都，其间主题几乎全是围绕吃来开展，所以到现在除了“好吃”，好像小编也不记得是什么味道了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image006.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1781\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image006.jpg\" alt=\"image006\" width=\"637\" height=\"477\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image006.jpg 637w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image006-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 637px) 100vw, 637px\" /></a></p>\n<p>倒是“怎么可以吃兔兔～”的兔头让人匪夷所思，看起来有点吓人，好几位同事不敢吃呢！</p>\n<p>第二天游黄龙溪古寨，也不知是谁看攻略说车费120，于是我们把4位的士司机师傅给忽悠了，打表跑138的路程，反正我们只给了120，至于一路上司机的吐槽已经不记得了（其实小编的内心几乎是狂喜的）。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image008.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1782\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image008.jpg\" alt=\"image008\" width=\"1018\" height=\"755\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image008.jpg 1018w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image008-300x222.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image008-777x576.jpg 777w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image010.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1783\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image010.jpg\" alt=\"image010\" width=\"998\" height=\"692\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image010.jpg 998w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image010-300x208.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image010-831x576.jpg 831w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px\" /></a>小编没学过摄影，但俺会画画</p>\n<p>三大炮、糖油果子、菠萝蒸饭、三合泥、一根面、军屯锅盔、伤心凉粉、开心冰粉，边走边吃几巴适哦！</p>\n<p>第三天去大熊猫基地，看这些圆滚滚、傻呆呆、萌萌哒国宝，园区里每一只熊猫都有独一无二的名字哦！可怎么我看他们好像都长一个样呢？</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image012.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1784\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image012.jpg\" alt=\"image012\" width=\"831\" height=\"619\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image012.jpg 831w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image012-300x223.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image012-773x576.jpg 773w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>感觉能够一直这样看他们吃竹笋、翻滚，一整天都不会无聊。</p>\n<p>即使是自由行，我们也不能放松警惕；在玩这方面，我们从来对自己都蛮狠！晚上大家唱歌到几近凌晨1点，第四天5点半爬起来向都江堰出发，一行有三位同事战斗到最后！</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image014.jpg\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-1785 aligncenter\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image014.jpg\" alt=\"image014\" width=\"716\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image014.jpg 716w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image014-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 716px) 100vw, 716px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image016.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1786\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image016.jpg\" alt=\"image016\" width=\"594\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image016.jpg 594w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image016-300x223.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 594px) 100vw, 594px\" /></a></p>\n<p>到都江堰感受古人的勤劳与智慧之后，爬到青城山上喝茶，虫鸣鸟叫、清风阵阵、茗香回味，这种闲适的感觉才是旅行的意义。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image018.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1787\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image018.jpg\" alt=\"image018\" width=\"662\" height=\"457\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image018.jpg 662w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image018-300x207.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 662px) 100vw, 662px\" /></a></p>\n<p>爬山途中目睹高水准搭讪技能，不失为此行中一道看点。又帮背包又要电话又搂拍合影，哈哈，一路见识后忍不住大呼：高手！</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image020.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1788\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image020.jpg\" alt=\"image020\" width=\"907\" height=\"510\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image020.jpg 907w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image020-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px\" /></a></p>\n<p>没去都江堰的同事在城区也没闲着，人民公园、宽窄巷子、杜甫草堂，放慢脚步游荡观赏，一边打望路上众帅哥美女。</p>\n<p>看到报纸上写成都第三届蝉联“全国文明城市”，就凭过斑马线小车司机会停下来让我，我也肯定这个称号名副其实了！友好、闲适、活力的城市气氛让我不禁想“少不入川”的说法真错了。</p>\n<p>行程最后一天（总编说此文像流水帐，开头不准再写“第五天”），踏上返程的路途，离开这座“来了就不想走的”城市——成都。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image022.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1789\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image022.jpg\" alt=\"image022\" width=\"831\" height=\"617\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image022.jpg 831w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image022-300x223.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/image022-776x576.jpg 776w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px\" /></a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2015/04/travel-in-chengdu/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3675143411","4019104361"]}